et-icon-box\" data-id=\"39903a8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tRelacionamentos\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRelacionamentos podem ser desafiadores, mas a boa not\u00edcia \u00e9 que \u00e9 poss\u00edvel transform\u00e1-los. \nNa terapia, vamos explorar juntos como fortalecer a comunica\u00e7\u00e3o e o entendimento m\u00fatuo, criando um espa\u00e7o de amor e respeito que te ajude a cultivar a rela\u00e7\u00e3o saud\u00e1vel que voc\u00ea tanto deseja.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba37dff elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"ba37dff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSexualidade\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tApesar da sexualidade ser uma parte essencial de quem somos, muitas mulheres enfrentam d\u00favidas, culpas e tabus que dificultam essa viv\u00eancia. Na minha pr\u00e1tica cl\u00ednica, ofere\u00e7o um espa\u00e7o acolhedor e seguro para que voc\u00ea explore essas quest\u00f5es com respeito e liberdade. Juntas, podemos ressignificar viv\u00eancias e fortalecer sua conex\u00e3o consigo mesma. Estou aqui para te apoiar nesse processo de autoconhecimento e reconex\u00e3o com a sua sexualidade.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3b15a343 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3b15a343\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-462c4766\" data-id=\"462c4766\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-3bb7e4b5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3bb7e4b5\" data-element_type=\"section\" id=\"certificados\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-169e2f45\" data-id=\"169e2f45\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-345e292a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"345e292a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Certificados<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div